category: Gnome
requires: libglade2.0_0 libatk1.0-devel libglib2.0-devel libgdk_pixbuf2.0-devel libgtk2.0-devel gettext libxml2-devel libpango1.0-devel python
external-source: libglade2.0
sdesc: "Library for runtime-loading Glade interfaces (development)"
ldesc: "Libglade is an alternative to using Glade's code generation. 
Instead of generating code from the XML interface description, libglade loads
and parses the description at runtime. It also provides functions that
can be used to connect signal handlers to parts of the interface."
